OL,3,CYoung adults trust group chats and
OL,4,CTikTok more than financial websites `
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FAlmost half (43%) of young Britons say
OL,8,Fthey trust financial tips shared in
OL,9,Ftheir group chats more than those
OL,10,Ffound on financial websites, a survey
OL,11,Fsuggests.
OL,13,FAlmost three quarters of 18 to 28-year-
OL,14,Folds (71%) use messaging apps and
OL,15,Fonline groups to find money-saving
OL,16,Ftips and tricks, the poll for
OL,17,FNationwide found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
