OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773637426
OL,3,CYoung adults trust group chats and
OL,4,CTikTok more than financial websites `
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FSome 36% use online group chats to
OL,8,Ffind discount codes, supermarket price
OL,9,Fdrops (30%) and restaurant deals
OL,10,F(22%), while 82% claim such spaces
OL,11,Fhave directly shaped their money-
OL,12,Fsaving habits.
OL,14,FThe poll found that 25 to 34-year-olds
OL,15,Fare aiming to save an average of
OL,16,F#7,536 this year.
OL,18,FMethods to save money included cutting
OL,19,Fback on nights out (37%) and taking on
OL,20,F"side hustles" (32%).
