OL,3,CYoung adults trust group chats and
OL,4,CTikTok more than financial websites `
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FOn average, 18 to 28-year-olds had
OL,8,Fsaved up to #512 a year as a result,
OL,9,Fmore than #200 more than their parents.
OL,11,FThe survey found many are also turning
OL,12,Fto social media for financial advice
OL,13,Fand practical money-saving strategies,
OL,14,Fwith 48% favouring TikTok.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
