OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773637426
OL,3,CYoung adults trust group chats and
OL,4,CTikTok more than financial websites `
OL,5,Cpoll
OL,7,FRichard Stocker, head of savings at
OL,8,FNationwide, said: "Young people are re-
OL,9,Fwriting the rulebook when it comes to
OL,10,Fmoney, and it's encouraging to see
OL,11,Fthem using social media not just for
OL,12,Fentertainment, but to learn, share
OL,13,Ftips, and support each other."
OL,15,FCensuswide surveyed 2,001 UK adults
OL,16,Fbetween February 11-13.
